    "custom_liquid_qmcpBp": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "t:names.custom_liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "{% comment %}\n  STUDIO SHOP — MASTER ARCHITECT STUDIO (PRINTFUL ZONE TEMPLATE BUILDER)\n  FULL COPY/PASTE REPLACEMENT\n\n  Purpose:\n  - Draw a precise \"zone\" box ON TOP of the product mockup image\n  - Lock the box to an exact aspect ratio defined by PRINTFUL print-area inches (W/H)\n  - Still allow move + resize visually, but resize stays ratio-locked when \"Lock ratio\" is ON\n  - Save as a PRODUCT TAG in the exact format Admin Powers already reads:\n      zone:TOP-LEFT-WIDTH-HEIGHT\n    (numbers only; values are percentages relative to the visible image canvas)\n\n  Notes:\n  - Studio does NOT render storefront logos.\n  - Zone is a reusable template (same for all stores).\n  - This ONLY saves the `zone:` tag. Your Make recipe system will store inch sizes later.\n\n  Requirements:\n  - Uses your existing Mechanic webhook (same as Admin Powers) to save tags.\n  - Your Mechanic task must support:\n      { action:\"set_zone_tag\", product_id:\"...\", zone_tag:\"zone:..-..-..-..\" }\n    If your Mechanic task currently only supports \"position_code\", paste it and I’ll update it.\n{% endcomment %}\n\n<div class=\"studio-container\">\n  <div class=\"header\">\n    <h1>📐 Master Architect Studio</h1>\n    <p>Build precise Printful zone templates (saved as <code>zone:TOP-LEFT-WIDTH-HEIGHT</code> tags).</p>\n    <p class=\"subtle\">Resize is ratio-locked using Printful inches. Move freely. Save writes a product tag Admin Powers reads.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n    {% paginate collections['all'].products by 50 %}\n      {% for p in collections['all'].products %}\n        {%- assign tags_lower = p.tags | join: ',' | downcase -%}\n        {%- unless tags_lower contains 'printful-template' -%}{% continue %}{%- endunless -%}\n\n        {% assign existing_zone = '' %}\n        {% for t in p.tags %}\n          {% assign tdown = t | downcase %}\n          {% if tdown contains 'zone:' %}\n            {% assign existing_zone = t %}\n          {% endif %}\n        {% endfor %}\n\n        <div class=\"card\">\n          <div class=\"media-wrap\" id=\"wrap-{{ p.id }}\">\n            <img\n              src=\"{{ p.featured_image | image_url: width: 900 }}\"\n              class=\"product-img\"\n              id=\"img-{{ p.id }}\"\n              alt=\"{{ p.title | escape }}\"\n              onload=\"SSStudio.resizeCanvas('{{ p.id }}')\"\n            >\n            <div class=\"canvas-layer\" id=\"canvas-{{ p.id }}\"></div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"controls\">\n            <div class=\"product-title\">{{ p.title }}</div>\n\n            <div class=\"meta\">\n              <span class=\"pill\">Product ID: {{ p.id }}</span>\n              {% if existing_zone != blank %}\n                <span class=\"pill pill--zone\">Current: {{ existing_zone }}</span>\n              {% else %}\n                <span class=\"pill pill--none\">Current: none</span>\n              {% endif %}\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"row\">\n              <label class=\"lbl\">Placement</label>\n              <select id=\"placement-{{ p.id }}\" class=\"select\" onchange=\"SSStudio.applyPlacement('{{ p.id }}')\">\n                <option value=\"front_xsm\">Front (XS–M) 11.5×13.8</option>\n                <option value=\"front_lplus\">Front (L+) 15×18</option>\n                <option value=\"back\">Back 12×16</option>\n                <option value=\"sleeve\">Sleeve 4×3.5</option>\n                <option value=\"outside_label\">Outside label 3×3</option>\n                <option value=\"custom\">Custom inches…</option>\n                <option value=\"free\">Freeform (no lock)</option>\n              </select>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"row row-3\">\n              <div class=\"field\">\n                <label class=\"lbl\">W (in)</label>\n                <input id=\"w-in-{{ p.id }}\" class=\"input\" type=\"number\" step=\"0.01\" value=\"11.50\" oninput=\"SSStudio.updateInches('{{ p.id }}')\">\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"field\">\n                <label class=\"lbl\">H (in)</label>\n                <input id=\"h-in-{{ p.id }}\" class=\"input\" type=\"number\" step=\"0.01\" value=\"13.80\" oninput=\"SSStudio.updateInches('{{ p.id }}')\">\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"field\">\n                <label class=\"lbl\">Lock</label>\n                <button id=\"lock-{{ p.id }}\" class=\"toggle is-on\" onclick=\"SSStudio.toggleLock(event, '{{ p.id }}')\">ON</button>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"row\">\n              <div class=\"pill pill--ratio\" id=\"ratio-pill-{{ p.id }}\">Ratio: 0.83</div>\n              <div class=\"pill pill--hint\">Resize stays locked when ON</div>\n            </div>\n\n            <button class=\"btn btn-draw\" onclick=\"SSStudio.initBox('{{ p.id }}')\">✏️ Draw Zone</button>\n            <button class=\"btn btn-save\" id=\"save-{{ p.id }}\" onclick=\"SSStudio.saveZone('{{ p.id }}', '{{ p.id }}')\">💾 Save Zone Tag</button>\n\n            <div class=\"hint\">\n              Drag box to move • Drag circle to resize • Locked resize uses W/H inches ratio • Save writes a single <code>zone:</code> tag.\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      {% endfor %}\n\n      {% if paginate.pages > 1 %}\n        <div class=\"pagination\">\n          {{ paginate | default_pagination }}\n        </div>\n      {% endif %}\n    {% endpaginate %}\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  .studio-container{max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,sans-serif}\n  .header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:22px}\n  .header h1{margin:0;font-size:24px;color:#222;font-weight:950;letter-spacing:-.02em}\n  .header p{margin:8px 0 0 0;color:#444}\n  .subtle{opacity:.75;font-size:13px}\n\n  .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(380px,1fr));gap:18px}\n  .card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e6e6e6;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.04)}\n\n  .media-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;height:470px;background:#f5f5f5;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;overflow:hidden}\n  .media-wrap img{width:auto;height:auto;max-width:100%;max-height:100%;display:block}\n\n  .canvas-layer{position:absolute;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.10);pointer-events:none;z-index:10}\n\n  .controls{padding:14px 14px 16px 14px;border-top:1px solid #eee;background:#fff;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}\n  .product-title{font-weight:950;font-size:15px}\n  .meta{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n\n  .pill{display:inline-block;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:999px;font-size:12px;border:1px solid #e6e6e6;background:#fafafa}\n  .pill--zone{border-color:#ffd2d2;background:#fff0f0}\n  .pill--none{opacity:.7}\n  .pill--ratio{border-color:#d7e7ff;background:#f1f7ff}\n  .pill--hint{opacity:.75}\n\n  .row{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}\n  .row-3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 90px;gap:10px;align-items:end}\n\n  .lbl{font-size:12px;font-weight:800;opacity:.75;display:block;margin-bottom:6px}\n  .select,.input{padding:10px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #ccc;font-size:13px;width:100%}\n  .field{display:flex;flex-direction:column}\n\n  .toggle{width:100%;padding:10px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #ddd;background:#f3f3f3;font-weight:950;cursor:pointer}\n  .toggle.is-on{background:#111;border-color:#111;color:#fff}\n\n  .btn{border:none;padding:12px;border-radius:10px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:950;font-size:13px;width:100%}\n  .btn-draw{background:#111;color:#fff}\n  .btn-save{background:#24a35a;color:#fff;display:none}\n  .btn-save:hover{filter:brightness(.95)}\n  .btn-save:disabled{background:#ccc;cursor:not-allowed}\n\n  .hint{font-size:12px;opacity:.75;line-height:1.25}\n  .pagination{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:10px;margin-top:34px}\n\n  /* Zone Box */\n  .zone-box{\n    position:absolute;\n    border:2px dashed #ff2a2a;\n    background:rgba(255,42,42,0.14);\n    cursor:grab;\n    pointer-events:auto;\n    z-index:100;\n    box-shadow:0 0 0 1200px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);\n    border-radius:4px;\n  }\n  .zone-handle{\n    width:16px;height:16px;background:#fff;border:2px solid #ff2a2a;\n    position:absolute;bottom:-9px;right:-9px;cursor:se-resize;border-radius:50%;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<script>\nwindow.SSStudio = (function(){\n  // ========= CONFIG =========\n  const MECHANIC_URL = \"https://webhooks.mechanic.dev/c47f1271-4902-40ac-bbb2-8a03c65932e8\";\n\n  // ========= STATE =========\n  const state = {}; // per productId: { lock:true/false, wIn, hIn }\n\n  const PLACEMENTS = {\n    front_xsm: { w: 11.5, h: 13.8 },\n    front_lplus: { w: 15, h: 18 },\n    back: { w: 12, h: 16 },\n    sleeve: { w: 4, h: 3.5 },\n    outside_label: { w: 3, h: 3 }\n  };\n\n  function el(id){ return document.getElementById(id); }\n\n  function ensureState(pid){\n    if(!state[pid]) state[pid] = { lock:true, wIn:11.5, hIn:13.8 };\n    return state[pid];\n  }\n\n  function setRatioPill(pid){\n    const s = ensureState(pid);\n    const pill = el('ratio-pill-' + pid);\n    const w = parseFloat(s.wIn) || 1;\n    const h = parseFloat(s.hIn) || 1;\n    const r = (h === 0) ? 0 : (w / h);\n    if(pill) pill.textContent = \"Ratio: \" + r.toFixed(2);\n  }\n\n  function resizeCanvas(pid){\n    const wrap = el('wrap-' + pid);\n    const img = el('img-' + pid);\n    const canvas = el('canvas-' + pid);\n    if(!wrap || !img || !canvas) return;\n\n    canvas.style.width = img.width + 'px';\n    canvas.style.height = img.height + 'px';\n    canvas.style.left = img.offsetLeft + 'px';\n    canvas.style.top = img.offsetTop + 'px';\n  }\n\n  function applyPlacement(pid){\n    const placement = el('placement-' + pid)?.value || 'front_xsm';\n    const s = ensureState(pid);\n\n    if(placement === 'free'){\n      s.lock = false;\n      const lockBtn = el('lock-' + pid);\n      if(lockBtn){ lockBtn.classList.remove('is-on'); lockBtn.textContent = 'OFF'; }\n      setRatioPill(pid);\n      return;\n    }\n\n    if(placement === 'custom'){\n      // keep current inputs, just ensure lock stays ON by default\n      s.lock = true;\n      const lockBtn = el('lock-' + pid);\n      if(lockBtn){ lockBtn.classList.add('is-on'); lockBtn.textContent = 'ON'; }\n      updateInches(pid);\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const def = PLACEMENTS[placement] || PLACEMENTS.front_xsm;\n    s.wIn = def.w;\n    s.hIn = def.h;\n    s.lock = true;\n\n    const wEl = el('w-in-' + pid);\n    const hEl = el('h-in-' + pid);\n    if(wEl) wEl.value = def.w;\n    if(hEl) hEl.value = def.h;\n\n    const lockBtn = el('lock-' + pid);\n    if(lockBtn){ lockBtn.classList.add('is-on'); lockBtn.textContent = 'ON'; }\n\n    setRatioPill(pid);\n    refreshBoxToLockedRatio(pid); // if box exists, snap it to new ratio\n  }\n\n  function updateInches(pid){\n    const s = ensureState(pid);\n    const wVal = parseFloat(el('w-in-' + pid)?.value || '0');\n    const hVal = parseFloat(el('h-in-' + pid)?.value || '0');\n    if(wVal > 0) s.wIn = wVal;\n    if(hVal > 0) s.hIn = hVal;\n    setRatioPill(pid);\n    refreshBoxToLockedRatio(pid);\n  }\n\n  function toggleLock(evt, pid){\n    evt.preventDefault();\n    const s = ensureState(pid);\n    s.lock = !s.lock;\n    const btn = el('lock-' + pid);\n    if(btn){\n      if(s.lock){\n        btn.classList.add('is-on'); btn.textContent = 'ON';\n        refreshBoxToLockedRatio(pid);\n      } else {\n        btn.classList.remove('is-on'); btn.textContent = 'OFF';\n      }\n    }\n  }\n\n  function initBox(pid){\n    resizeCanvas(pid);\n\n    const canvas = el('canvas-' + pid);\n    if(!canvas) return alert('Canvas not found');\n    if(canvas.querySelector('.zone-box')) return;\n\n    ensureState(pid);\n    setRatioPill(pid);\n\n    const s = state[pid];\n\n    const box = document.createElement('div');\n    box.className = 'zone-box';\n\n    // Start width = 45% of visible image\n    const startWpx = Math.max(140, canvas.offsetWidth * 0.45);\n    let startHpx = Math.max(140, canvas.offsetHeight * 0.45);\n\n    if(s.lock){\n      const ratio = (parseFloat(s.wIn) || 1) / (parseFloat(s.hIn) || 1);\n      startHpx = startWpx / ratio;\n    }\n\n    box.style.left = '27%';\n    box.style.top = '18%';\n    box.style.width = (startWpx / canvas.offsetWidth * 100) + '%';\n    box.style.height = (startHpx / canvas.offsetHeight * 100) + '%';\n\n    box.innerHTML = '<div class=\"zone-handle\"></div>';\n    canvas.appendChild(box);\n\n    makeDraggable(box, canvas, pid);\n    const saveBtn = el('save-' + pid);\n    if(saveBtn) saveBtn.style.display = 'block';\n  }\n\n  function refreshBoxToLockedRatio(pid){\n    const s = ensureState(pid);\n    if(!s.lock) return;\n\n    const canvas = el('canvas-' + pid);\n    const box = canvas?.querySelector('.zone-box');\n    if(!canvas || !box) return;\n\n    const ratio = (parseFloat(s.wIn) || 1) / (parseFloat(s.hIn) || 1);\n    if(!isFinite(ratio) || ratio <= 0) return;\n\n    // Keep current WIDTH % the same; adjust HEIGHT % to match ratio\n    const wPct = parseFloat(box.style.width) || (box.getBoundingClientRect().width / canvas.getBoundingClientRect().width * 100);\n    const canvasRect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();\n    const wPx = (wPct / 100) * canvasRect.width;\n    const hPx = wPx / ratio;\n    const hPct = (hPx / canvasRect.height) * 100;\n\n    box.style.height = hPct + '%';\n  }\n\n  function makeDraggable(elBox, parent, pid){\n    let isResizing = false;\n\n    elBox.addEventListener('mousedown', start);\n    elBox.addEventListener('touchstart', start, {passive:false});\n\n    function start(e){\n      e.preventDefault(); e.stopPropagation();\n      const pt = e.touches ? e.touches[0] : e;\n\n      isResizing = e.target.classList.contains('zone-handle');\n\n      const startX = pt.clientX, startY = pt.clientY;\n      const rect = elBox.getBoundingClientRect();\n      const pRect = parent.getBoundingClientRect();\n      const startW = rect.width, startH = rect.height;\n      const startL = rect.left - pRect.left, startT = rect.top - pRect.top;\n\n      function move(e){\n        if(e.cancelable) e.preventDefault();\n        const pt = e.touches ? e.touches[0] : e;\n        const dx = pt.clientX - startX;\n        const dy = pt.clientY - startY;\n\n        if(isResizing){\n          const s = ensureState(pid);\n\n          let newW = Math.max(40, startW + dx);\n          let newH;\n\n          if(s.lock){\n            const ratio = (parseFloat(s.wIn) || 1) / (parseFloat(s.hIn) || 1);\n            newH = newW / ratio;\n          } else {\n            newH = Math.max(40, startH + dy);\n          }\n\n          elBox.style.width  = (newW / pRect.width) * 100 + '%';\n          elBox.style.height = (newH / pRect.height) * 100 + '%';\n        } else {\n          elBox.style.left = ((startL + dx) / pRect.width) * 100 + '%';\n          elBox.style.top  = ((startT + dy) / pRect.height) * 100 + '%';\n        }\n      }\n\n      function stop(){\n        window.removeEventListener('mousemove', move);\n        window.removeEventListener('mouseup', stop);\n        window.removeEventListener('touchmove', move);\n        window.removeEventListener('touchend', stop);\n      }\n\n      window.addEventListener('mousemove', move);\n      window.addEventListener('mouseup', stop);\n      window.addEventListener('touchmove', move, {passive:false});\n      window.addEventListener('touchend', stop);\n    }\n  }\n\n  function calcZoneTag(pid){\n    const canvas = el('canvas-' + pid);\n    const box = canvas?.querySelector('.zone-box');\n    if(!canvas || !box) return null;\n\n    const pRect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();\n    const bRect = box.getBoundingClientRect();\n\n    const topPct = ((bRect.top - pRect.top) / pRect.height * 100);\n    const leftPct = ((bRect.left - pRect.left) / pRect.width * 100);\n    const widthPct = (bRect.width / pRect.width * 100);\n    const heightPct = (bRect.height / pRect.height * 100);\n\n    // Admin Powers reads: zone:top-left-width-height\n    return \"zone:\" +\n      topPct.toFixed(2) + \"-\" +\n      leftPct.toFixed(2) + \"-\" +\n      widthPct.toFixed(2) + \"-\" +\n      heightPct.toFixed(2);\n  }\n\n  async function saveZone(cardId, productId){\n    const btn = el('save-' + cardId);\n    const zoneTag = calcZoneTag(cardId);\n    if(!zoneTag){\n      alert('Draw a zone first.');\n      return;\n    }\n\n    btn.textContent = \"Saving…\";\n    btn.disabled = true;\n\n    try{\n      const res = await fetch(MECHANIC_URL, {\n        method:'POST',\n        headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},\n        body: JSON.stringify({\n          action: \"set_zone_tag\",\n          product_id: String(productId),\n          zone_tag: zoneTag\n        })\n      });\n\n      if(!res.ok){\n        const t = await res.text();\n        throw new Error(\"Mechanic error: \" + t);\n      }\n\n      btn.textContent = \"Saved ✅\";\n      btn.style.background = \"#111\";\n    } catch(err){\n      console.error(err);\n      alert(\"Save failed. Check Mechanic Events for errors.\\n\\n\" + err.message);\n      btn.textContent = \"Error ❌\";\n      btn.disabled = false;\n    }\n  }\n\n  // init all canvases on load & resize\n  window.addEventListener('load', function(){\n    document.querySelectorAll('.media-wrap').forEach(w=>{\n      const id = w.id.replace('wrap-','');\n      resizeCanvas(id);\n      ensureState(id);\n      setRatioPill(id);\n      applyPlacement(id);\n    });\n  });\n\n  window.addEventListener('resize', function(){\n    document.querySelectorAll('.media-wrap').forEach(w=>{\n      const id = w.id.replace('wrap-','');\n      resizeCanvas(id);\n    });\n  });\n\n  // public\n  return {\n    resizeCanvas,\n    initBox,\n    saveZone,\n    applyPlacement,\n    updateInches,\n    toggleLock\n  };\n})();\n</script>",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "padding-block-start": 0,
        "padding-block-end": 0
      }
    }
  },
